Boris Johnson wants to spend £900,000 to repaint his plane in the colours of the union flag. It is inconsiderate and inappropriate to be wasting taxpayers money at a time when so many people have been hugely effected by Covid 19 and faced many hardships because of the pandemic. It is unjustifiable when the Government has forced austerity on us for so many years; this money could be better spent elsewhere.

For reference;

https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-53082294
